-\frac{\csc\theta}{9} = -\frac{\sqrt{x^2 + 9}}{9x}
x = 3tanθ
tanθ = x/3 = opp/adj
= - sqrt[ 1+cot^2(t)] / 9  = - sqrt[ 1+ 1/tan^2(t)] /9  = -sqrt[ 1+ 1/(x/3)^2]  = -sqrt[ 1+9/x^2] /9 = - sqrt(9+x^2) / 9x + C 
